en she should take a ceramic vessel and should write AL-MATEE-NO on it with the first rainwater then recite this dua and drink this water then inshallah the milk will be sufficient…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Agar kisi khaatoon ka doodh bachche ke liye kam ho to us ko chahiye keh ek cheeni (ceramic) ke bartan par aabe nisa (pehli baarish ka paani) ke saath AL-MATEE-NO likkhe aur us bartan par yeh dua padhe. Phir us paani ko aurat pee-le to us ka doodh inshallah ul azeez ziyadah ho jaayega…", "UrduDescription": "اگر کسی خاتون کا دودھ بچے کے لئے کم ہو تو اس کو چاہئے کہ ایک چینی کے برتن پر آب نیساء کے ساتھ ’’اَلْمَتِیْنُ‘‘ لکھے اور اس برتن پر یہ دعا پڑھے، پھر اس پانی کو عورت پی لے تو اس کا دودھ انشاء اللہ العزیز زیادہ ہوجائے گا، اس عمل کے مجرب ہونے کا دعویٰ کیا جاتا ہے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "Arabi